Title: The Woman King
Plot: The Sagittarons allege that a doctor is discriminating against them. As Helo investigates, he becomes concerned that the doctor may even be murdering patients. Meanwhile, Athena unwittingly brings Hera to the doctor for treatment.
GuestStars: Gabrielle Rose, Ryan Robbins, Bruce Davison, Nicki Clyne, Donnelly Rhodes, Kandyse McClure, Alessandro Juliani, Richard Hatch
